- New Garden level with pool party and tons of stuff to destroy and new features:
 * Pool that you can swim in
 * Cats that will follow you
- Performance improvements

-Shopping Mall Update!  2 new levels - huge market and a restaurant.
-Over 40 new interactions - act as a real cat ! 
-4 new cats : Zebra, Smokey and a mighty Tiger along with itâ€™s cub.
